-- Pertamina Picks Three Banks for Sale of Dollar-Denominated Bonds
-- B y   T a n y a   A n g e r e r
-- 2012-03-21T02:55:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-21/pertamina-picks-three-banks-for-sale-of-dollar-denominated-bonds.html
PT Pertamina picked Barclays Plc,
Citigroup Inc. and  HSBC Holdings Plc (HSBA)  to arrange its planned U.S.
dollar-denominated bonds, according to Mohamad Afdal Bahaudin,
director for planning and risk management at the company.  To contact the reporter on this story:
